-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note on DataWarp driver
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

DataWarp driver relies on ncmpio driver to write/read NetCDF files
DataWarp driver uses subroutines of ncmpio driver internally.
Whever the structure of PNC_Driver changes, not only the interface of DataWarp
driver needs to be updated but also its internal ncmpio driver related codes.

Known issue in DataWarp driver:
1. vard API is not supported. It will be forward to ncmpio directly.

